Metadata.Title: Kill Order: IAGO Trators
Metadata.Description: Greetings 47 you have been contracted today by Viktor Novikov & Dalia Margolis to eliminate the trator and the trators conspirators Dalia has learned Hailey Brennan who works for her is betraying her.Hailey actually works for Valerie St.Claire and her back up if she fails is Liza Mckenzie they both was invited tonight to the Party by Viktor so they can be handled tonight.They also found out Jaques Rosso & Loic CouRcelle gave them access to IAGO remove them 47 end there lives.
